        <p class="text-center fs-5 fw-semibold text-primary mt-4">"Getting Started with Power Apps: Setting up Your Environment"</p>
        <p>Create or Sign In to Your Microsoft Account: The first step in your Power Apps journey is to ensure you have a Microsoft account. If you already have one with appropriate <span style="color:red;font-weight:500">PowerApps license</span>, you can simply log in using your existing credentials on <a href="http://make.powerapps.com/" target="_blank" class="text-decoration-none">make.powerapps.com</a>.</p>
        <p class="text-center fw-semibold">“For more information about PowerApps license you can visit <a href="https://powerapps.microsoft.com/en-us/pricing/" target="_blank" class="text-decoration-none">https://powerapps.microsoft.com/en-us/pricing/</a>"</p>
        
