        <ul class="gap-3"><li>Go to the Microsoft developer Account Creation Page: Visit the Microsoft account creation page (<a href="https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/dev-program" target="_blank" class="text-decoration-none">https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/dev-program</a>) in your web browser. </li>
            <li>Click on "Join now” button to begin the registration process for Power Apps Developer Program.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center mt-4 mb-4"><img src="~/images/learn/getting started with power apps/1. how to sign in/screenshot_1.png" alt="Setting up and creating Microsoft 365 Developers Account" class="img-fluid" width="100%" /></div>
