        </ul>
        <div class="container d-flex flex-lg-row justify-content-center mt-4 mb-4">
            <img src="~/images/learn/getting started with power apps/1. how to sign in/screenshot_4.png" alt="Setting up and creating Microsoft 365 Developers Account" class="img-fluid me-2" width="50%" />
            <img src="~/images/learn/getting started with power apps/1. how to sign in/screenshot_5.png" alt="Setting up and creating Microsoft 365 Developers Account" class="img-fluid" width="50%" />
