        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center mt-4 mb-4"><img src="~/images/learn/getting started with power apps/1. how to sign in/screenshot_9.png" alt="Setting up and creating Microsoft 365 Developers Account" class="img-fluid" /></div>
        <ul><li>You have successfully configured Microsoft 365 developer account. Just copy the email which is generated by Microsoft.</li></ul>
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center mt-4 mb-4"><img src="~/images/learn/getting started with power apps/1. how to sign in/screenshot_10.png" alt="Setting up and creating Microsoft 365 Developers Account" class="img-fluid" /></div>
